public class GnRole
extends GnDataObject

Represents the role that a contributor played in a music or video production; for example, singing, playing an instrument, acting, directing, and so on.

Note:

For music credits, the absence of a role for a person indicates that person is the primary artist, who may have performed multiple roles.
